Package com.thomsonreuters.upa.rdm Description

This package provides the definitions for Reuters Domain Models (RDM) as regards the Open Message Model (OMM). RDM conformant data is available via Thomson Reuters Enterprise Platform for Real-Time (TREP-RT), EleKtron, and Reuters Data Feed Direct (RDFD) using the Ultra Performance API (UPA).
